column2: SELECT    m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1,    n.objid, n.distance,    o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2,   o.modelMag_u as u, o.modelMagErr_u as u_err,   o.modelMag_g as g, o.modelMagErr_g as g_err,   o.modelMag_r as r, o.modelMagErr_r as r_err,   o.modelMag_i as i, o.modelMagErr_i as i_err,   o.modelMag_z as z, o.modelMagErr_z as z_err into mydb.MyTable_# from MyDB.spectro_stripe AS m     OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n     LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid=o.objid
